AmeriHealth has cheap rates with Silver plans starting at $488 per month, just $6 more than Horizon BCBS, and they also have the most affordable Bronze plans in New Jersey at $391 per month on average Best Cheap Health Insurance in New Jersey (2025) - ValuePenguin. However, AmeriHealth gets more complaints about its health insurance plans than some competitors Best Cheap Health Insurance in New Jersey (2025) - ValuePenguin.
