TAX BENEFITS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT
Small Business Health Care Tax Credit: Worth up to 50% of premiums paid if you have fewer than 25 employees with average wages under $50,000 GetCoveredNJ | Small Employers/SHOP. With 2 employees, you likely qualify for partial credit.
Premium Deductibility: All premiums you pay are 100% tax-deductible as a business expense.
Employee Pre-Tax Contributions: Employee premium contributions come out pre-tax, reducing their taxable income.
Section 125 Plan: Set up a Section 125 cafeteria plan so employees can pay their portion pre-tax (saves ~25-30% in taxes for the employee).
